ye samāveśamayapraśastabhaktiyuktāḥ ata eva labdhatvatsaṃpadaḥ tvatpureviśvapūrake tvatsvarūpe vasanti tacchīlāḥ teṣāṃ lokamārge api yaḥ sañcāraḥ vyavahāraḥ, sa tayaiva samāveśarasānandamayyā, vijṛmbhayā vikasvaratayā syāt bhavatyeva | atha ca ye labdhalaukikaśriyaḥ tvadbhaktāḥ tvanmaṇḍalavāsinaḥ te sarve spṛhaṇīyatvāt sadā vibhūtimuditā iti samāsoktyā gamayati |

<commentary>bhaktimatāṃ vyākhyātarūpabhaktiśālināṃ sarvatra bhuvanaviṣaye kiṃ na kṣetraṃ parasiddhisamudayasthānam, kva ca eṣāṃ mananatrāṇadharmo mantro na siddhyati | yataḥ sākṣāditi samāveśadṛṣṭyā na kathāmātreṇa bhavanmayameva sarvaṃ bhuvanameṣām |
</commentary>

jayanti bhakti iti | bhaktipīyūṣarasa evāsavavaraḥ - utkṛṣṭaṃ pānaṃ, tena udgataharṣā ye te jayanti — sarvotkarṣeṇa vartante | kīdṛśāḥ |